criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male workers;

          -  Age between 20 and 60 years;

          -  Have been working night shift for at least six months;

          -  Sedentary.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Failure to provide the information or material necessary for the development of the
             study;

          -  Carriers of diseases previously diagnosed and under treatment, such as type 2 diabetes
             mellitus, hypertension, cardiovascular diseases and related mood disorders such as
             depression.
